                                                                                         </svg>
                                                                                     </a>
				</h1>
				<div class="actions-group">
					<Button><a href="/projects" class="actions">View My Work</a></Button>
					<Button><a href="/resume.pdf" class="actions">View My Resume</a></Button>
				</div>
			</div>
	</body>
</html>
